data.description: Welcome to the ideal home in the heart of tranquility! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom property invites you to experience the epitome of modern living. Nestled in a quiet and cozy neighborhood, this residence exudes warmth and charm from the moment you step through the door.  The main floor has undergone a stunning transformation, featuring a captivating fireplace that serves as the focal point of the spacious living area. The luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring seamlessly flows throughout, offering both durability and a touch of contemporary elegance. Natural light floods the living spaces and the updated lighting fixtures add a touch of sophistication creating an atmosphere that is both inviting and stylish. The space has been professionally painted, providing a cohesive and refreshing palette that complements the home's modern aesthetic. French doors open to a charming outdoor space, extending the living area to the fresh air and sunshine.  The well-designed layout includes three generously sized bedrooms. The master suite is a private oasis, complete with lofty ceilings, a walk in closet and ensuite bathroom. One of the secondary bedrooms is a unique retreat with a vaulted ceiling, creating an airy and spacious ambiance. This architectural feature adds character and individuality, making it a perfect space for creativity, relaxation, or rejuvenation  Convenience is at your doorstep with this property's prime location. Just one mile away, you'll find a shopping mall, grocery store, and a fitness gym. Easy access to Highway 285 is and this home is located within close proximity to Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning remodeled property your new home. Embrace the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience in this idyllic neighborhood. Schedule a showing today and step into the lifestyle you've been dreaming of!
